title: Creamy Cheese Sausage , Tortellini and Mushrooms with Spinach and Pine Nuts
description: Creamy, indulgent and quick to prepare – what more could we want from a fuss-free weeknight meal? We guarantee you'll scarf down this beautiful bowl of al dente tortellini that's tossed in a luscious mushroom-sausage sauce and topped with toasted pine nuts.

