l peppers, cabbage, celery, tomato, garlic), hydrolyzed vegetable proteins (corn, soy), potato starch, palm oil, corn starch, yeast extract, canola oil, spice extracts, herb, turmeric extract, natural flavour) (soy, sulphites) • Chives • Lemon-pepper seasoning (sugar (sugar, maltodextrin), black pepper, salt, granulated garlic, lemon juice powder (corn syrup solids, lemon juice solids, lemon oil, silicon dioxide), lemon peel granules, spices, herbs, citric acid, canola oil, silicon dioxide).
